import React from 'react'
import { Container ,Navbars  ,Nav ,NavBrand ,NavText,NavImg,Loginin ,NavLink ,Link ,Signin,Signup} from './style'
import log from '../../Rasim/logo.png'
const Navbar = () => {
    return (
       <Container>
            <Navbars>
               <Nav>

                  <NavBrand> 
                        <NavImg  src={logo}/>
                       <NavText>antools.</NavText>
                  </NavBrand>
                   
                  <NavLink>
                          <Link>Home</Link>
                          <Link>Categories</Link>
                          <Link>My Collections</Link>
                          <Link>Blog</Link>
                  </NavLink>
                     
                  <Loginin>
                     <Signin>Login</Signin>
                     <Signup>Sign Up</Signup>
                  </Loginin>
               </Nav>
            </Navbars>
       </Container>
    )
}

export default Navbar
